<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Workflow Architect - EdTech Instructional Design</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #0f172a;
            --bg-card: #1e293b;
            --primary: #38bdf8;
            --primary-hover: #0ea5e9;
            --success: #34d399;
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --border: #334155;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 100%);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        header h1 {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 3fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .stage-card {
            background-color: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .stage-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .stage-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .stage-title {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .badge {
            background: #334155;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--success);
        }

        .grid-2 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .grid-2 {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .section-box {
            background: #151f32;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .prompt-box {
            background: #0b111e;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: monospace;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border: 1px dashed var(--border);
            position: relative;
        }

        .sidebar {
            position: sticky;
            top: 20px;
            height: fit-content;
        }

        .widget {
            background-color: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .widget h3 {
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        button {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: #0f172a;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-hover);
        }

        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100px;
            background: #0f172a;
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 10px;
            resize: none;
        }

        .checkbox-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .summary-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 100%);
            border: 1px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        @media print {
            body { background: white; color: black; }
            .sidebar, button { display: none; }
            .stage-card { page-break-inside: avoid; border: 1px solid #ccc; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>AI Workflow Architect</h1>
        <p>End-to-End EdTech Content Creation & Instructional Design Workflow</p>
        <button onclick="window.print()" style="width: auto; margin-top: 15px; padding: 8px 16px;">🖨️ Print Workflow Guide</button>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- Main Workflow Section -->
        <main>
            <!-- STAGE 1 -->
            <div class="stage-card">
                <div class="stage-header">
                    <h2 class="stage-title">Stage 1: Curriculum Planning & Analysis</h2>
                    <span class="badge">Est. Time: 4-6 Hours</span>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-2">
                    <div class="section-box">
                        <strong>🎯 Objectives:</strong>
                        <p>Define learning personas, bridge skill gaps, and map complete course syllabus structures aligned with target industry trends.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-box">
                        <strong>🛠️ Recommended AI Stack:</strong>
                        <p><strong>Claude 3.5 Sonnet:</strong> Best for deep pedagogical analysis, structuring logical learning taxonomies, and creating user personas.</p>
                        <p><em>Alternatives: ChatGPT Plus, Perplexity AI</em></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-2">
                    <div>
                        <strong>📋 Tasks:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Analyze target audience demographics.</li>
                            <li>Perform industry skill-gap mapping.</li>
                            <li>Generate high-level module architecture.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>⚠️ Common Mistakes:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Making modules too broad or lengthy.</li>
                            <li>Ignoring the prior knowledge level of users.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <strong>💡 Actionable AI Prompt Example:</strong>
                <div class="prompt-box">
                    "Act as an expert EdTech Instructional Designer. I need to design a 4-week crash course on 'Generative AI Applications for Marketing Professionals'. Create a target persona outline, identify 5 core skill gaps, and structure a complete 4-week curriculum blueprint with micro-learning milestones using Bloom's Taxonomy."
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- STAGE 2 -->
            <div class="stage-card">
                <div class="stage-header">
                    <h2 class="stage-title">Stage 2: Scripting & Storyboarding</h2>
                    <span class="badge">Est. Time: 8-12 Hours</span>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-2">
                    <div class="section-box">
                        <strong>🎯 Objectives:</strong>
                        <p>Convert core modular educational strategies into highly engaging conversational video scripts and dynamic visual storyboards.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-box">
                        <strong>🛠️ Recommended AI Stack:</strong>
                        <p><strong>ChatGPT (GPT-4o):</strong> Best for writing rapid, creative conversational outlines, interactive quiz variations, and video scene prompts.</p>
                        <p><em>Alternatives: Claude, NotebookLM</em></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-2">
                    <div>
                        <strong>📋 Tasks:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Write explicit hook-driven scripts.</li>
                            <li>Design visuals layouts for slide transitions.</li>
                            <li>Embed formative assessment questions.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>⚠️ Common Mistakes:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Overcrowding presentation slides with heavy text.</li>
                            <li>Lacking clear calls-to-action at lesson ends.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <strong>💡 Actionable AI Prompt Example:</strong>
                <div class="prompt-box">
